---
import BlogLayout from '../layouts/BlogLayout.astro';
import { User, Code, Heart, Coffee } from 'lucide-react';
---

<BlogLayout title="关于我 - 轩仔的博客" description="关于博主轩仔的个人介绍。">
  <div class="max-w-2xl">
    <header class="mb-12">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">关于我</h1>
      <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg">
        <p class="lead">
          嗨，我是轩仔。一名热爱折腾的全栈开发者，目前专注于 Node.js 生态与前端工程化。
        </p>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="space-y-12">
      <section>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <div class="p-2 bg-primary-500/10 rounded-lg text-primary-400">
            <Code className="w-6 h-6" />
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">技术栈</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="bg-dark-800/50 p-4 rounded-xl border border-dark-800">
            <h3 class="font-medium text-white mb-2">Frontend</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">React, Vue, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, Next.js</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-dark-800/50 p-4 rounded-xl border border-dark-800">
            <h3 class="font-medium text-white mb-2">Backend</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Node.js, NestJS, PostgreSQL, Redis, Docker</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <div class="p-2 bg-purple-500/10 rounded-lg text-purple-400">
            <Heart className="w-6 h-6" />
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">博客初衷</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="prose prose-invert text-gray-400">
          <p>
            建立这个博客的初衷很简单，就是想在这个碎片化的时代，保留一块属于自己的静谧之地。
          </p>
          <p>
            这里不仅会有硬核的技术干货，也会有我对生活的碎碎念。我相信技术是为了更好地生活，而写作是为了更好地思考。
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <div class="p-2 bg-emerald-500/10 rounded-lg text-emerald-400">
            <Coffee className="w-6 h-6" />
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">联系我</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-dark-800/30 rounded-xl p-6 border border-dark-800">
          <p class="text-gray-400 mb-4">
            如果你对我的文章感兴趣，或者想和我探讨技术问题，欢迎通过以下方式联系我：
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
            <li>
              <span class="text-gray-500 w-20 inline-block">Email:</span>
              <a href="mailto:hi@example.com" class="text-primary-400 hover:text-primary-300 transition-colors">hi@example.com</a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="text-gray-500 w-20 inline-block">GitHub:</span>
              <a href="https://github.com" target="_blank" class="text-primary-400 hover:text-primary-300 transition-colors">@xuanzai</a>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</BlogLayout>
